<br>
I have been leading or joining Kael Drakkal raid about 7 times.<br>
<br>
At the first attempt, we could get only one piece during 3 hours. As I wrote, a piece dropped near the bank in Kael. I think that we didn't know its drop point well.<br>
<br>
And at the second attempt, we tried mobs in Arena. We couldn't get anything. I think that pulling from Arena is worthless for getting armor pieces. Though we killed some fighters, inspectors, and guards of Arena, we couldn't get any special stuffs.<br>
<br>
But we tried the new area at the third attempt, we got some armor pieces from giants.<br>
The following picture contains some information of it.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://yulle.mpogfan.com/cgi/zboard/data/995962586/arena_black.jpg"><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--> <br>
<br>
<br>
The final camping spot is marked as &quot;CAMP SPOT 3&quot;. I think that this point is good place for farming armor pieces.<br>
But you need camp a while at another each camp spots.(CAMP SPOT 1, CAMP SPOT 2....)<br>
<br>
You can get some armor pieces from Veteran, Trooper(so rare),Protectors of Rallos Zek, and etc., so on at &quot;Camp Spot 3&quot; easily.<br>
<br>
I suggest making 2 groups with high level tanker for that. You will conflict 51-57 giants repeatly. And you need a skillful monk as main puller. (When we farmed armor pieces, almost guys are level 51+, and there are four level 60 players including a warlord.)<br>
<br>
Also while you camp at &quot;Camp Spot 3&quot;, you can try more nasty mobs. -- We couldn't try inside of temple area yet.<br>
<br>
But if your group want to take some armor pieces, then just try Veterans or Troopers for safe. They will drop well than you thought. (At least, they did for my case. We found random armor piece every 1 hour.)<br>
<br>
I got the new armor piece(Torn Enchanted Glove) tonight. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Note 1 : You need clearing each camp spot in 17 min.<br>
Note 2 : CR in Kael is so hard. You must recruit a rogue for that.(But also dangerous for them)<br>
<br>
